{"title":"Semiologia ORL Mod1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología/Semiologia ORL Mod1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Semiologia ORL\\NGeriatrica - Modulo 1","guid":"DB7f1X4D4vS8Ig290pOYUQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"1.1 Historia Clinica\\NOrientada al AM","guid":"Pccb-_kN9hhw7MA1Hrii9Q","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Comorbilidades → POLIFARMACIA, DM, HTA, cardiopatia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Estado cognitivo y funcional PREVIO al examen","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Interrogatorio\\Ndirigido","guid":"IHDC_8kNCeAOPlV9zQ55Zg","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Hipoacusia → impacto comunicacional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"Disfagia → riesgo aspiracion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"Disfonia → >1 mes = ALERTA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"4","text":"Vertigo/inestabilidad → riesgo caidas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"4","text":"Epistaxis → anticoagulantes, fragilidad mucosa","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Factores psicologicos → siempre preguntar (Matamala)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"Dar diagnostico o sospecha, pronostico, posibilidad de contacto","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"0","text":"1.2 Examen Fisico\\NORL Sistematico","guid":"I9pfN1pGpIE9_NHqkTuzMw","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"ORDEN: oido → nariz → boca/garganta → laringe → cuello","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"Oido Externo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Inspeccion: pabellon auricular completo (anterior + posterior)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"Referencias: helix, trago, antitrago, lobulo (sin cartilago)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"Buscar lesiones actinicas → queratosis, CBC, CEC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"12","text":"Otoscopia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"CAE → cerumen impactado frecuente en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"Membrana\\Ntimpanica","guid":"OoM_LFbNawxVeOJuOM5TRw","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"Pars flacida (superior) y pars tensa (inferior)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"Cono luminoso → cuadrante anteroinferior","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"Mango del martillo, umbus, apofisis corta","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"20","text":"4 cuadrantes: anterosuperior, anteroinferior, posterosuperior, posteroinferior","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"18","text":"EN AM: atrofia CAE → mayor impactacion cerumen","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"12","text":"Rinoscopia\\NAnterior","guid":"7_mAMoXYACiG4q86Oxhdmg","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Fosa nasal = piramide truncada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Piso = paladar duro, techo = lamina cribosa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"3 pares de cornetes → medio e inferior permanentes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"EN AM: mucosa atrofica, seca, costras","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"Descenso punta nasal → debilitamiento cartilago","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"12","text":"Orofaringoscopia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Inspeccion cavidad oral + orofaringe","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Pedir movimiento lingual → evaluar glosofaringeo (IX par)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"Bajalenguas en tercio posterior","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"EN AM: protesis dental dificulta examen, xerostomia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"12","text":"Rinofaringe","guid":"","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Examen con espejo o fibroscopio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"12","text":"Laringoscopia\\NIndirecta","guid":"fEr1hiRXQlrF4S71cexGIQ","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"Espejo laringeo → imagen invertida","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"Estructuras: epiglotis, bandas ventriculares, cuerdas vocales, aritenoides, senos piriformes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"Fibroscopio flexible → imagen anatomica directa, no requiere traccion lingual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"39","text":"EN AM: osificacion cartilaginosa, atrofia pliegues vocales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"12","text":"Cuello","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"Palpacion sistematica de cadenas ganglionares","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"Glandulas salivales → atrofia con edad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"ATM → crepitacion, subluxacion en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"Tiroides","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"12","text":"Consideraciones\\NPracticas en AM","guid":"JPapHWNkeHF19k2ZYphnKw","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Deterioro cognitivo → menor cooperacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"Hipoacusia → dar instrucciones claras y cercanas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"Protesis dental → retirar para examen oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"49","text":"Fragilidad → posicionar cuidadosamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"49","text":"TIEMPO → examen mas lento, ser paciente","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"0","text":"1.3 Examenes\\NComplementarios","guid":"dolarh5X-RbLb734UVvOcA","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Audiometria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Tonal → rojo derecho, azul izquierdo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Logoaudiometria → comprension verbal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"EN AM: patron presbiacusia → caida frecuencias altas bilateral simetrica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"55","text":"Imagenologia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Rx lateral huesos propios y CPN → preferir DIGITAL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"TAC oidos, CPN, cuello → GOLD STANDARD anatomico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"RNM oidos, CPN, cuello → tejidos blandos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"Angioresonancia arterias cerebrales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"60","text":"Ecografia → tiroides, glandulas salivales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"60","text":"PET-CT → mejor para identificar primarios ocultos y secundarios","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"55","text":"Tecnicas\\NDiagnosticas\\NNasales","guid":"kjRTd6MvWgaJ4X4hADz46Q","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Transiluminacion → limitada utilidad actual","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Puncion seno maxilar → poco frecuente hoy","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Rinomanometria → resistencia flujo aereo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"55","text":"Laringoscopia\\NAvanzada","guid":"HTtg3X_gqo7h_lcBnePCwQ","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"Telelaringoscopia → traccion lingual, menor especificidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"Fibroscopia flexible → anatomica, sin traccion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"71","text":"Estroboscopia → vibracion mucosa, lesiones sutiles","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"0","text":"1.4 Cambios del\\NEnvejecimiento en\\NORL","guid":"B7DCbYD4Ljl-iv8-ZqwWPw","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"CONCEPTO: PRESBI- = envejecimiento funcional de cada sistema","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"Oido\\NExterno","guid":"9aiYCe3Ihf2uZOadXYObUQ","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"Pabellon: trastornos actinicos frecuentes (CBC, CEC)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"Proteccion solar → RECOMENDACION","guid":"13DHcHDK0n6j46tcO-Nw2A","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"CAE: disminucion produccion cerumen + cerumen mas seco","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"77","text":"Piel CAE atrofica → prurito, fragilidad, laceraciones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"77","text":"Emolientes topicos recomendados","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"75","text":"Oido Medio\\Ne Interno","guid":"vWIbEOBY-Smw91uWgI5oEA","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Presbiacusia → ~2/3 adultos >70 anios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"Hipoacusia neurosensorial bilateral simetrica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"Mecanismo multifactorial: degeneracion + ruido + genetica + enfermedad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"83","text":"IMPACTO: deterioro cognitivo, demencia, depresion, aislamiento, caidas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"83","text":"Sintomas vestibulares en >50% AM","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"75","text":"Nariz y Senos Paranasales\\N(PRESBYNASALIS)","guid":"XT2zmQ7SQZRRKD2EOeilSA","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Cartilago adelgaza y pierde elasticidad → descenso punta nasal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"Musculatura facial se atrofia → menor soporte","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"Columela se retrae","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"89","text":"Mucosa nasal atrofica → sequedad, costras, epistaxis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"89","text":"Volumenes nasales AUMENTAN pero resistencia tambien aumenta (paradoja)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"89","text":"Mucosa menos elastica (especialmente postmenopausia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"89","text":"Cilios: menor frecuencia de batido → clearance reducido","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"89","text":"Rinorrea senil: 72% >85a vs 8% jovenes (estudio Pittsburgh)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"89","text":">60% rinitis en AM es NO ALERGICA → inmunosenescencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"89","text":"Secreciones mas espesas → goteo postnasal, carraspeo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"75","text":"Disfuncion Olfatoria\\N(PRESBYOSMIA)","guid":"ow_XuXJDHy44klyOKTi5xA","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Declive progresivo desde 6a decada, acelerado >70a","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"50% adultos >60 anios con disfuncion olfatoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"Hendidura olfatoria aumenta volumen con edad (Worley 2018)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"Perdida selectividad neuronal olfatoria + cambios centrales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"100","text":"ASOCIACION CRITICA: biomarcador precoz Alzheimer, Parkinson, DCLewy","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"100","text":"Predictor mortalidad a 5 anios en AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"100","text":"Manejo: counseling seguridad (humo, gas, alimentos), entrenamiento olfatorio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"75","text":"Laringe (ENVEJECIMIENTO\\NLARINGEO)","guid":"I6sxlGwOPd9h1y4vL2pzwQ","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Osificacion cartilagos → inicia 6a decada, variable entre sexos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"Cartilago tiroides: central en hombres, superior en mujeres","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"Cricoides: osificacion casi completa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"Aritenoides: cuerpo y apofisis muscular osifican, apex cartilaginoso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"108","text":"Articulacion cricoaritenoidea → cambios degenerativos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"108","text":"Descenso laringeo en el cuello → altera resonancia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"108","text":"Atrofia pliegues vocales → gap glotico, insuficiencia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"108","text":"Lamina propia adelgaza (especialmente hombres)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"108","text":"Colageno desorganizado → 7% mayor atrofia por cada anio de edad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"108","text":"Resultado: PRESBIFONIA (voz tremula, debil, ronca)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"75","text":"Mucosa Oral y\\NGlandulas Salivales","guid":"YZnoAA4fCkRTKAld15x-Bg","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Atrofia mucosa oral → dolor, vulnerabilidad a lesiones","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"Glandulas salivales → menor lubricacion → XEROSTOMIA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"119","text":"Resorcion osea alveolar → afecta resonancia vocal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"119","text":"Protesis mal ajustadas → dolor, parestesias, afectan fonacion","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"75","text":"Musculatura\\NDeglutoria","guid":"8lmynYfb1KT-01ZqHGh2tw","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"Atrofia musculos masticatorios y linguales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"Menor area seccional transversal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"124","text":"Deglucion mas lenta, respuesta faringea retardada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"124","text":"= PRESBIFAGIA (cambio normal vs disfagia patologica)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"75","text":"Tabla 12.2 Brocklehurst:\\NFactores que Afectan Calidad\\NVocal","guid":"pv6uAR3NiyBWWknfUm9Zhw","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"Atrofia/fibrosis muscular laringea → gap glotico, perdida aerea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"129","text":"Cambios articulacion cricoaritenoidea → osificacion altera resonancia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"129","text":"Atrofia mucosa → riesgo lesion, dolor, afecta articulacion","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"129","text":"Atrofia glandulas salivales → boca seca, problemas dentales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"129","text":"Resorcion osea alveolar → altera resonancia del habla","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"129","text":"Cambios tracto respiratorio inferior → menor elasticidad toracica, fatiga vocal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"129","text":"Perdida dental/gingival → afecta sonidos plosivos, fricativos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"129","text":"Enfermedad ATM → crepitacion, limita apertura oral","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClinicas","guid":"94ZXJCRlFS4bBnhB0ovh_Q","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"En AM con hipoacusia: whispered voice test como screening rapido en VGI","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"Cerumen impactado = causa tratable de hipoacusia → SIEMPRE revisar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"Disfonia >1 mes en fumador >60a = fibroscopia OBLIGATORIA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"138","text":"Disfuncion olfatoria en AM: pensar en neurodegeneracion ANTES que en causa local","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"138","text":"Rinorrea acuosa persistente en AM: probable no alergica → ipratropio nasal util","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"138","text":"Xerostomia: revisar lista de farmacos (anticolinergicos, diureticos, antidepresivos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"138","text":"Examen ORL en AM con demencia: adaptar, ser paciente, retirar protesis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"138","text":"Presbifagia =/= disfagia patologica → distinguir para no sobretratar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"138","text":"Screening sensorial en VGI: audicion + olfato + deglucion = MINIMO","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"0","text":"VER\\NTAMBIEN","guid":"ZA4UPQ4_YvHhmtPW2LTNlA","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"→ Presbiacusia y Oido Externo (Modulo 2 ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"→ Presbynasalis y Olfato (Modulo 3 ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"→ Presbifonia y Cancer Laringeo (Modulo 4 ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"148","text":"→ Presbifagia y Deglucion (Modulo 5 ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"→ VGI Completa (Geriatria)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"148","text":"→ Polifarmacia y STOPP-START (Farmacologia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"148","text":"→ Screening Sensorial en VGI (Modulo 7 ORL)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"1. Bareiss A, Nieman CL, Emmett SD. Otolaryngology in Older Adults. En: Brocklehurst's Textbook of Geriatric Medicine. Cap 12.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"2. Matamala. Clase Semiologia ORL y Diagnostico. 2014.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"3. Matamala. Clase Oido Externo. 2015.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"156","text":"4. DelGaudio JM, Panella NJ. Presbynasalis. Int Forum Allergy Rhinol. 2016;6(10):1083-87.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"156","text":"5. Worley ML et al. Age-related differences in olfactory cleft volume. Laryngoscope. 2019;129(2):E55-E60.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"156","text":"6. de Araujo Pernambuco L et al. Prevalence of voice disorders in the elderly: systematic review. Eur Arch Otorhinolaryngol. 2015;272:2601-09.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"156","text":"7. Correa A. Manual de Otorrinolaringologia. Mediterraneo, 1999.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":163,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"ORL","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología","filename":"Semiologia ORL Mod1","id":"map_1618","resolved_references":[]}